    "MissionGiver": "Citizens for Prosperity",
    "Title": "Get Back at XenoThreat",
    "Description": "Hey,\n\nXenoThreat just raided one of our convoys and made off with a bunch of supplies. I\u2019m not sure exactly where they took them, but I know they have a cache of stolen cargo not too far away. If I had to guess, that\u2019s exactly where they took them. \n\nThe spot is ~mission(Location|Address). Need someone to go there, grab the goods inside, and bring them to ~mission(Destination|Address). The outpost is a little ways away from their main operations hub. Normally, there\u2019s fewer forces there than the main outpost, but don\u2019t think this will be a walk in the park. Just be smart and prepared. \n\nBe safe, \n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
